  "pluginNotes": "Tree is a SAP instance. Plugin places it via SAP_KEYS lookup. Tree contents are TreeItem children — for now, spec must enumerate items explicitly. Plugin does not auto-detach Tree to inject custom items; specs should pass a flat items[] array with level/parent metadata and let the plugin compose TreeItem instances.",
